Bill of materials:
	* STM32F407 (ARM M4 - Digikey)<br/>
	* L9616 (CAN transceiver - Digikey))<br/>
	* CSD88599Q5DC (half bridges - Digikey)<br/>
	* DRV 8302 (FET pre driver - Digikey)<br/>
	* Power off brakes (Ali)<br/>
	* Outrunner Brushless motors (Ali)<br/>
	* iC-MHM from iC-Haus (14 bit absolute magnetic encoder)<br/>
	* RGB ring (smart RGB addressable, controlled by a STM32F103 to keep the motor controller focusing only on the motor)
